summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Seattle-King County Department of Public Health; amending SMC 0.03.140 to specify the fee to be charged for immunizations other than travel-related and influenza immunizations; adding a new section, Section 10.03.150, to the Seattle Municipal Code to establish fees for travel-related immunizations and services; and repealing Ordinances 105145, 98610, 105146 and 109496.
